OL,3,CTwo prisoners seen entering inmate's
OL,4,Ccell before 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,FTwo prisoners who kicked and stamped
OL,7,Fanother inmate to death in his cell
OL,8,Fwill be staying in jail for at least a
OL,9,Fdecade longer.
OL,11,FAshirie Smith, 19, and Thierry
OL,12,FRobinson, 21, were seen on CCTV
OL,13,Fwalking into Mahir Abdulrahman's
OL,14,Funlocked cell, and coming back out 30
OL,15,Fseconds later after carrying out the
OL,16,Fattack at HMP Fosse Way.
