OL,3,CTwo prisoners seen entering inmate's
OL,4,Ccell before 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,FSmith has been given a life sentence
OL,7,Ffor murder, with a minimum of 17.5
OL,8,Fyears. Robinson, who had been due to
OL,9,Fbe released, was jailed for 11 years
OL,10,Ffor manslaughter.
OL,12,FThe 31-year-old victim had suffered
OL,13,Fweeks of taunts and abuse by the pair,
OL,14,Fincluding physical attacks, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FIn August last year, Mr Abdulrahman
OL,18,Fhad thrown a kettle of hot water,
OL,19,Fwhich hit both men, through a gap in
OL,20,Fhis cell door.
