OL,3,CTwo prisoners seen entering inmate's
OL,4,Ccell before 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,FThe next morning, a grinning Robinson,
OL,7,Fclad in a dressing gown, was seen on
OL,8,FCCTV walking to Smith's cell.
OL,10,FRobinson appears to keep watch of the
OL,11,Fhallway and Abdulrahman's cell. A
OL,12,Ftopless Smith then emerges, before the
OL,13,Fpair walk into their victim's room,
OL,14,Fwhich had been unlocked by an officer
OL,15,Fdoing their rounds.
OL,17,FTwo other people appear to be in the
OL,18,Fhallway as the attack happens.
