OL,6,FLess than a minute later, Smith and
OL,7,FRobinson walk out, with Smith
OL,8,Fappearing to rub his hands and
OL,9,Fknuckles.
OL,11,FA prison officer found Mr Abdulrahman
OL,12,Fwith severe head injuries after being
OL,13,Fkicked and having his neck stamped on.
OL,14,FHe was later pronounced dead at the
OL,15,Fscene.
OL,17,FThe judge said that inside the cell
OL,18,Fthere was "ferocious violence" and
OL,19,F"copious" amounts of blood after the
OL,20,Fbeating Mohammed received.
