OL,6,FSmith was serving a three-year
OL,7,Fsentence for firearms offences. He was
OL,8,Falso sentenced this week for a violent
OL,9,Frobbery at the home of a De Montfort
OL,10,FUniversity student in Leicester in
OL,11,FMarch 2023.
OL,13,FRobinson had been serving a 5.5 year
OL,14,Fsentence for drug offences. He had
OL,15,Fbeen due for release in late 2024.
