OL,3,CTwo prisoners seen entering inmate's
OL,4,Ccell before 'ferocious' attack
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mark Parish, from
OL,7,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,8,FUnit, said: "The injuries showed a
OL,9,Fserious, sustained attack had taken
OL,10,Fplace which ultimately led to his
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"Thanks to the hard work of the
OL,14,Finvestigation team, Smith and Robinson
OL,15,Fhave been convicted in court and will
OL,16,Fnow have to face responsibility for
OL,17,Ftheir actions."
OL,19,FA third defendant Shaan Karim, 38, was
OL,20,Ffound not guilty of murder and not
OL,21,Fguilty of manslaughter.
